WEBVTT

00:00:01.120 --> 00:00:03.416
"These are the times,"

00:00:03.440 --> 00:00:05.456
said Thomas Paine,

00:00:05.480 --> 00:00:07.360
"that try men's souls."

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:09.616
And they're trying ours now.

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:13.816
This is a fateful moment
in the history of the West.

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:18.840
We've seen divisive elections
and divided societies.

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:21.240
We've seen a growth of extremism

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:24.160
in politics and religion,

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:28.280
all of it fueled by anxiety,
uncertainty and fear,

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:34.456
of a world that's changing
almost faster than we can bear,